\f2\b0  These are analysts applying frameworks to primary data. Their value is proportional to the rigor of their methodology and the verifiability of their historical accuracy. Use Tier 1 experts identified in Part II.\

\f1\b Tertiary Market Signal Sources
\f2\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
